data.description: IF YOU LOVE MARDI GRAS IN SHREVEPORT THEN YOU WILL WANT TO JUMP ON THIS ONE! THIS PRECIOUS COTTAGE IN BROADMOOR IS STEPS AWAY FROM THE PARADE ROUTE AND FEATURES A LIVING ROOM, FORMAL DINING ROOM, EAT IN KITCHEN, SEPARATE DEN OR SUNROOM, 3 BEDROOMS, 2 BATHS AND OVER 2290 SQUARE FEET. BEAUTIFUL ORIGINAL HARDWOOD FLOORS GLEM THROUGHOUT THE HOME. THE EXTRA LARGE PRIMARY BEDROOM FEATURES A SITTING AREA AND AN UPDATED EN SUITE BATH. THE KITCHEN FEATURES A LOT OF COUNTER SPACE, STORAGE, DOUBLE OVEN AND EXTRA SEATING. THE DOUBLE LOT IS PERFECT FOR OUTDOOR ENTERTAINING ESPECIALLY IN THE BEAUTIFUL OUTDOOR COVERED STRUCTURE - PERFECT FOR ANY OCCASION. HUGE FLOORED ATTIC . DON'T MISS OUT, SET UP YOUR APPT TO SEE THIS PRECIOUS HOME TODAY.
